Package api.equinix.javasdk.fabric.enums

package api.equinix.javasdk.fabric.enums
Fabric-specific enumerations for the Equinix Java SDK. Defines typed constants for connection states (ConnectionState), connection statuses (ConnectionStatus), port types (PortType), change types (ChangeType), charge frequencies (ChargeFrequency), network types, cloud router states, routing protocol types, stream states, route filter actions, precision time types, and other Fabric domain values.
